children.subject: What is the eligibility for this opportunity?

history.content:
Hi,

We are currently searching for a UGSI/GSI for CS294-082. This will most likely be  > 10 hours role, which means fee remission :) as well. Please let me know if you are interested. We have strong preference for those who have taken the course in the past.

raymondchong@berkeley.edu
